<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 23 日星期二 03:42:09 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[US Smuggler Who Claims CIA Backed His Kurdish Gun Factory Convicted of Torture]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110529395" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105974/58/1059745868_0:0:1920:953_1440x900_80_0_1_1b53139f996aa21b9642b9ca9506e523.jpg?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1059745867" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/us-smuggler-who-claims-cia-backed-his-kurdish-gun-factory-convicted-of-torture-1110529395.html?share-img=1059745867"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> //</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">囚犯</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="Prisoner - Sputnik International, 1920, 23.05.2023" title="囚犯" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105974/58/1059745868_113:0:1807:953_1920x0_80_0_0_32ce2c56ad35a2463f462c00838e90ce.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105974/58/1059745868_113:0:1807:953_640x0_80_0_0_8f227df7409c1ecea0bad55af8e7167b.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105974/58/1059745868_113:0:1807:953_1280x0_80_0_0_5b3a27b24a57418c0100e6f840ac3f5b.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105974/58/1059745868_113:0:1807:953_1920x0_80_0_0_32ce2c56ad35a2463f462c00838e90ce.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">悦里德</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_wyatt_reed/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">一名多年来一直试图为伊拉克的库尔德分离分子制造非法武器的骗子很可能面临终身监禁。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国司法部周一发布消息称，一名来自宾夕法尼亚州的 54 岁前伞兵因涉嫌绑架和虐待非法武器工厂的一名雇员而被判犯有酷刑罪，该工厂旨在向伊拉克的库尔德分离分子提供枪支有详细的。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">陪审团周五一致裁定罗吉奥犯有 39 项酷刑、走私武器、电汇欺诈和洗钱罪，这些罪名的总刑期超过 700 年。量刑指南表明，罗吉奥在 8 月宣判时可能会被判处无期徒刑。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>美国司法部发布的一份<u><a href="https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/man-convicted-torture-and-exporting-weapons-parts-and-related-services-iraq" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">新闻稿</a></u>称，罗焦“安排库尔德士兵将受害者绑架并拘留在库尔德军事大院”，肇事者“用皮带勒死受害者，威胁要切断他的一根手指，并指示库尔德人在 39 天的时间里，士兵们反复殴打、骚扰、扼杀受害者，以及以其他方式对受害者进行身心虐待。”</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “受害者受雇于 Roggio 在伊拉克库尔德斯坦地区开发的一家武器工厂，该工厂旨在制造 M4 自动步枪和 Glock 9 毫米手枪，”声明解释说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “关于武器工厂项目，其中包括 Roggio 向外国人提供 M4 自动步枪的操作、组装和制造方面的培训，Roggio 还非法出口了由国务院和商务部控制出口的枪支零件， ”司法部写道。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>该新闻稿详细说明了该判决，标志着自 1994 年联邦立法实施以来第二位被判犯有酷刑罪的美国被告。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在担任该职务之前，罗焦曾参与多项有法律问题的金融计划，包括涉嫌企图诈骗多个商业伙伴。在他的枪支公司倒闭之前，他在北卡罗来纳州费耶特维尔的特种部队避风港度过了数年，然后消失在海地，在那里他被指控挪用一家旨在帮助海地地震受害者的慈善机构的物资。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">罗焦于 2014 年首次来到伊拉克，当时他被特种部队指挥官波拉德·塔拉巴尼 (Polad Talabani) 带入伊拉克制造手枪和突击步枪，塔拉巴尼是被称为库尔德斯坦爱国联盟的库尔德政治王朝的继承人。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">检察官说，当他在埃尔比勒着陆时，罗焦带来了黏糊糊的手指。他们声称他“挪用了数百万美元，用于购买制造设备，用于个人开支，包括劳力士手表和跑车，”一家美国媒体解释说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>据报道，自始至终，雷焦坚称他的行动得到了中央情报局的支持。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在他第一次明显企图将枪支制造材料走私到伊拉克而被捕后，雷吉奥坚称审问他的特工没有适当的“许可级别”来继续谈话。他随后声称该机构指示他将情报传递给塔拉巴尼。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">罗焦提交的法律文件称，美国驻库尔德首府埃尔比勒总领事肯·格罗斯授权他建造武器工厂。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 23 May 2023 03:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/us-smuggler-who-claims-cia-backed-his-kurdish-gun-factory-convicted-of-torture-1110529395.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/us-smuggler-who-claims-cia-backed-his-kurdish-gun-factory-convicted-of-torture-1110529395.html<category>世界</category><category>我们</category><category>走私者</category><category>宾夕法尼亚州</category><category>伊拉克</category><category>美国司法部</category><category>定罪</category><category>酷刑</category><category>中央情报局 (CIA) </category></item><item><title><![CDATA[U-Haul Truck Crashes Near White House Security Barrier, Nearby Buildings Evacuated]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110529214" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/08/1099394415_0:0:3077:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_b2c805f5adcd6817a8408805c8a4cb67.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1099394398" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/u-haul-truck-crashes-near-white-house-security-barrier-nearby-buildings-evacuated-1110529214.html?share-img=1099394398"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Natalia Seliverstova</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">美国总统官邸，华盛顿特区的白宫</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Official residence of the U.S. President, the White House in Washington D.C. - Sputnik International, 1920, 23.05.2023" title="美国总统官邸，位于华盛顿特区的白宫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/08/1099394415_0:159:3077:1890_1920x0_80_0_0_19ef6748a02fe8652b94afa7ddbe8243.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/08/1099394415_0:159:3077:1890_640x0_80_0_0_2c8630cc11dcd82157bdefc405268013.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/08/1099394415_0:159:3077:1890_1280x0_80_0_0_887faa5618550f5148088db6aac90d48.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/08/1099394415_0:159:3077:1890_1920x0_80_0_0_19ef6748a02fe8652b94afa7ddbe8243.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Natalia Seliverstova </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__supplemented"><span class="point"></span>更新中</div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周一晚些时候，一辆 U-Haul 卡车撞上了白宫附近的安全屏障，促使官员疏散附近的建筑物。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">执法人员没有详细说明动机；然而，当地媒体报道称，司机已被拘留。现场没有人员伤亡报告。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">事件发生在白宫北面的拉斐特广场附近。附近地区的几座建筑物要么被封锁，要么被急救人员疏散。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此后，社交媒体上出现了一段视频，显示远处的卡车。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">证人分享了一个 Uhaul 试图在拉斐特广场（靠近白宫北草坪）的理由<br><br>瑞吉酒店的工作人员告诉我，道路已经疏散并封锁。 <a href="https://t.co/KUg7qg43Ks">pic.twitter.com/KUg7qg43Ks</a></p> - AJD (@ASHLEYJDIMELLA) <a href="https://twitter.com/ASHLEYJDIMELLA/status/1660833218319245313?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 23 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当局现在正在调查据报道在晚上 10 点之前发生的 U-Haul 卡车撞车事故后留下的“可疑包裹”。当局关闭了 H 街的几个街区以进行<a href="https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/u-haul-crashes-into-barrier-near-white-house-authorities/3353262/" target="_blank">调查</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">更多细节即将到来。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 23 May 2023 03:16:34 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/u-haul-truck-crashes-near-white-house-security-barrier-nearby-buildings-evacuated-1110529214.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/u-haul-truck-crashes-near-white-house-security-barrier-nearby-buildings-evacuated-1110529214.html<category>美洲</category><category>白色的房子</category><category>我们</category><category>碰撞</category><category>私人服务</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hungary Signs Gas Purchase Agreement With Qatar]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110528939" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/1a/1092527755_0:0:2917:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_1b4ce97beeb1ab5ced104c663ebea243.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1092527751" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/hungary-signs-gas-purchase-agreement-with-qatar-1110528939.html?share-img=1092527751"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">卡塔尔液化天然气 (LNG) 油轮在卡塔尔北部拉斯拉凡斯海港装载液化天然气</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt=" Qatari liquid natural gas (LNG) tanker ship being loaded up with LNG at Raslaffans Sea Port, northern Qatar - Sputnik International, 1920, 23.05.2023" title="卡塔尔液化天然气 (LNG) 油轮在卡塔尔北部拉斯拉凡斯海港装载液化天然气" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/1a/1092527755_0:82:2917:1723_1920x0_80_0_0_54fc667f84bedbde43b4b50e1ea706ae.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/1a/1092527755_0:82:2917:1723_640x0_80_0_0_5dbeda2f01374e4c2a650c248addab23.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/1a/1092527755_0:82:2917:1723_1280x0_80_0_0_9b198f7c525b225aa921b68268c572ff.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/1a/1092527755_0:82:2917:1723_1920x0_80_0_0_54fc667f84bedbde43b4b50e1ea706ae.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据布达佩斯（人造卫星）网报道：匈牙利总理维克多·欧尔班在与卡塔尔埃米尔谢赫·塔米姆·本·哈马德·阿勒萨尼会谈后表示，匈牙利已与卡塔尔签署了购买天然气的协议，两国计划发展经济合作。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “在过去的一年里，我们了解到卡塔尔是一个对欧洲至关重要的国家。欧洲经济用来自这里的液化天然气弥补了俄罗斯天然气缺失的很大一部分......我们就能源合作达成一致，我们也将从这里购买天然气 - 多条腿站立总比一条腿站立好， ”欧尔班在 Facebook* 上发布的来自多哈的视频消息中说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他还说，经过会谈，匈牙利和卡塔尔领导人还同意发展基础设施和空中交通，在通信和农业领域开展合作，为卡匈经济合作开辟了良好前景。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">匈牙利总理还表示，卡塔尔和匈牙利一样，准备在乌克兰问题的和平解决中进行调解。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">匈牙利外交部多次表示，匈牙利正在努力使该国的天然气供应多样化，但短期内不可能取代俄罗斯的能源。除了增加阿塞拜疆天然气的进口，匈牙利还有兴趣通过克罗地亚克尔克的终端增加对该国的液化天然气供应，并在罗马尼亚开发一个气田。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，根据匈牙利外交部长彼得·西雅尔托的说法，作为供应多元化的一部分，布达佩斯正在考虑从厄瓜多尔进口石油的可能性，以防俄罗斯石油无法通过乌克兰陆路运输。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此前，西雅尔托表示，他在访问卡塔尔首都多哈期间签署了一项协议，根据该协议，匈牙利和卡塔尔的能源公司可能会在大约三年后就向匈牙利供应液化天然气展开谈判。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据他介绍，匈牙利和阿曼合作伙伴之间也在专家和企业层面就可能开始从阿曼进口石油和天然气进行谈判。西雅尔托强调，与海湾国家就向匈牙利供应石油和天然气达成协议并不意味着放弃与俄罗斯的合同，而是为了多元化。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>*在俄罗斯因极端主义而被禁止</em></div></div></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 23 May 2023 02:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/hungary-signs-gas-purchase-agreement-with-qatar-1110528939.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230523/hungary-signs-gas-purchase-agreement-with-qatar-1110528939.html<category>世界</category><category>匈牙利</category><category>维克托欧尔班</category><category>塔米姆·本·哈马德·阿勒萨尼</category><category>液化天然气</category><category>液化天然气 (LNG)</category><category>匈牙利外交部</category><category>彼得西雅托</category><category>卡塔尔</category><category>俄罗斯</category></item></channel></rss>